<li id="cite_note-6"><b><a href="#cite_ref-6" title="">^</a></b> Thus n.1 to the www.perseus.tufts.edu English translation of the <i>Poetics</i><a href="http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/cgi-bin/ptext?doc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.01.0056;query=section%3D%2313;layout=;loc=1452b#anch1" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/cgi-bin/ptext?doc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.01.0056;query=section%3D%2313;layout=;loc=1452b#anch1" rel="nofollow">[1]</a>.</li>
<li id="cite_note-7"><b><a href="#cite_ref-7" title="">^</a></b> R. Caldwell ("The Pattern of Aeschylean Tragedy," <i>TAPA</i> 101 (1970), pp. 77-94) cites with approval the conventional wisdom that the <a href="/wiki/Persians" title="Persians" class="mw-redirect">Persians</a> "is the one play in the entire extant literature - not just in Aeschylus - which is genuinely and fully founded upon hubris."</li>
<li id="cite_note-8"><b><a href="#cite_ref-8" title="">^</a></b> Struck 2000 <a href="http://www.classics.upenn.edu/myth/tragedy/oedhero.php" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.classics.upenn.edu/myth/tragedy/oedhero.php" rel="nofollow">[2]</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-9"><b><a href="#cite_ref-9" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=QUTuvcB68DEC&amp;pg=PA377&amp;lpg=PA377&amp;dq=hamartia+hamartoma&amp;source=web&amp;ots=PRBtaWxWBL&amp;sig=xoueqxp01Boh8j-dEAEpsK96Stg#PPA377,M1" class="external free" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=QUTuvcB68DEC&amp;pg=PA377&amp;lpg=PA377&amp;dq=hamartia+hamartoma&amp;source=web&amp;ots=PRBtaWxWBL&amp;sig=xoueqxp01Boh8j-dEAEpsK96Stg#PPA377,M1" rel="nofollow">http://books.google.com/books?id=QUTuvcB68DEC&amp;pg=PA377&amp;lpg=PA377&amp;dq=hamartia+hamartoma&amp;source=web&amp;ots=PRBtaWxWBL&amp;sig=xoueqxp01Boh8j-dEAEpsK96Stg#PPA377,M1</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-10"><b><a href="#cite_ref-10" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.mercksource.com/pp/us/cns/cns_hl_dorlands.jspzQzpgzEzzSzppdocszSzuszSzcommonzSzdorlandszSzdorlandzSzdmd_h_02zPzhtm" class="external text" title="http://www.mercksource.com/pp/us/cns/cns_hl_dorlands.jspzQzpgzEzzSzppdocszSzuszSzcommonzSzdorlandszSzdorlandzSzdmd_h_02zPzhtm" rel="nofollow">Dorlands Medical Dictionary</a></li>
</ol>
